name: "CLONE VENUS" SERIES Artwork of Takeru Amano, Created and enhanced by APPortfolio

metadata.name: 0001 A Bitter Sweet Goodbye
metadata.description:
Artelli presents: "Attack of Clone Venus" Exhibition Debut in Macau. "CLONE VENUS" takes on AI technology that reorganizes the artist's masterpiece "VENUS" series and decompose it as a theme, thereby developed the first batch of 450 digital collections accompanied by physical works.
